{"tid":1379823,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母","createTime":"2019-07-29T00:50:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T16:01:28.000Z","uid":98167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8ba64560ad62d0288c2ca9063f1dbd5e1ed41486","tid":1379823,"uid":98167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:50:02.000Z","msg":"屌屌屌！！！！！！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"edd6c502813a27c2670472ed783d9adee0e00f1b","tid":1379823,"uid":156632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:51:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">疑似水軍<br />\n請勿回覆呢類型垃圾帖 負評都不要<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日3pm港澳辦開記招 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">今日一定好多水軍洗版帶風向想分化各位手足<br />\n呢場運動之所以仲繼續到落去全賴大家學識不割蓆 所以唔好被輕易帶動<br />\n邊個話袋住先就屌鳩佢老母<br />\n遇到啲講錯嘢嘅手足要予以糾正 以防更多人受影響<br />\n</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n遇到三毛 上一頁 唔好推唔好負評有佢沉 <br />\n三毛特癥：<br />\n-禁入個po冇內容可言/得幾隻字<br />\n-標題黨<br />\n-p牌<br />\n<br />\n死左咁多、拉左咁多義士要我地算數？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一路走來咁辛苦唔好輕易退讓 <br />\n我地要一齊實現五大訴求加清算警隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n不分化不割蓆<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n有關聽日港澳辦開會事情，大家聽我講講。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378852</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n不割蓆不篤灰只係理念唔係絕對 唔好俾呢樣嘢騎劫！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379750\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379750</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2d001337c9cc28842e7a14ff04a6cc3e87a39f42","tid":1379823,"uid":24824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:01:28.000Z","msg":"食撚屎啦"}]}